lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ea151b82bd879af95908eaf53ef160c4d3a236","tid":642173,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"今日講故仔係8148 , 講完之後即刻散貨，而家插緊61%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 散貨散到咁出面我真係五體投地"},{"pid":"61ca4c9a6fdae37bb4ae024d986e82dcadeb9a87","tid":642173,"uid":25256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:51:16.000Z","msg":"佢啲小說都唔錯 碳60"},{"pid":"741171f5944068925727da4b63c76b7edb81eb91","tid":642173,"uid":52904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T08:08:46.000Z","msg":"講股佬嚟講最憎呢條友<br />\n做埋咁多推人接火棒嘅濕鳩野然後日日寫野顯示自己幾有品味(實情好撚low)<br />\n其他財演都只係廢，佢直頭係噁心<br />\n<br />\n利申，無跟過佢買任何一隻股票"},{"pid":"9f9c99f3369a1e2e042741896da91c4fd512f97a","tid":642173,"uid":46077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"差唔多十年啦，跟佢買276，半個月袋一百萬"},{"pid":"1b9d4faa7cf626719ffad904e7b78ec16efe0a7f","tid":642173,"uid":172442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"市况不明，但寶申控股卻如此受歡迎，有點不尋常，但是，上周五時它的暗盤價卻跌了4%，本着《大時代》中陳萬賢的「人棄我取」的大原則，這更加吸引了我的注意。<br />\n<br />\n結果判斷沒錯，它升至0.5元收市，贏了十多個巴仙，成交只有6000萬元，但我仍未沽出，皆因看走勢，它的升幅遠不止於此，且看這一次我的看法準不準？能否再贏錢。<br />\n<br />\n[周顯 投資二三事]"},{"pid":"d5ef9c3d49ee8a207e1c2a2e6a5e94f2bc3e73dd","tid":642173,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f9c99f3369a1e2e042741896da91c4fd512f97a","tid":642173,"uid":46077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"差唔多十年啦，跟佢買276，半個月袋一百萬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"鋪排黎, 開頭唔放堅料點上位"},{"pid":"d830dfa09db19eb3bc730155fa8ade3128c50206","tid"